# Game Studio Brainstorming Template

## Studio Name Ideas
- **Primary Ideas:**
  - Obsidian
  - Onyx Games
  - Magno Entertainment
- **Alternative Ideas:**
  - Camstar Games
  - Basalt Interactive
  - NightRealm Games

- Chosen Name - CamStar
- About the name - I like the punchy feel it has and the double syllable of CamStar. Cam is the name my friends call me sometimes because I use it as a username in games and Star is something flashy I wanted at the end as well.
- Social Medias available - TikTok, Instagram
- Possible Domain Names - camstar.com; camstar.co; camstarinteractive.com; camstar.games; camstar.studio; 

---

## Vision Statement
At CamStar we create worlds that captivate, challenge and inspire. 
Where every story is more than just entertainment; they are experiences that transport players to places both familiar and unknown. 
Our vision is to forge games that resonante with our players and leave them with a sense of wonder and a lasting connection to the stories we bring to life.

